es.\n\n5. **Clarification on "Sequential Pipeline"**: In Step 6, you suggest passing only stable materials to the mechanical classifier. \n   - **Suggestion**: Be careful with this. Many metastable materials (energy_above_hull > 0) are still mechanically stable and experimentally synthesizable. By filtering out all metastable materials, you might discard valid candidates. Consider running the mechanical classifier on the *entire* dataset and using the stability score as a secondary filter or a weighted component of the final ranking score.' additional_kwargs={} response_metadata={} id='77bda010-c7c1-4638-ae02-f8766c68f5ee'



